This directory contains variants of the MD code
that introduce various optimizations.

ljmd-c.c:  baseline c code
ljmd-c1.c: apply newton's 3rd law (F_ij = -F_ji)
ljmd-c2.c: avoid using expensive math. pow(), sqrt(), divisions
ljmd-c3.c: move invariant expressions outside of loops.

ljmd-f.f90:  baseline fortran code
ljmd-f1.f90: fortran version with all optimizations.

bonus
ljmd-cc.c:   using cell-lists to avoid O(N**2) scaling.
ljmd-fc.f90: fortran version of the cell-list code

